org.batfish.representation.cisco.nx

Class CiscoNxBgpVrfConfiguration

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.batfish.representation.cisco.nx.CiscoNxBgpVrfConfiguration
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public final class CiscoNxBgpVrfConfiguration
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Represents the top-level configuration of a VRF in a BGP process for Cisco NX-OS.

    Configuration commands that can be entered at the config-router (for default VRF) or config-router-vrf levels are VRF-specific BGP configuration.

    See Also:
